rows.label: tev017701_MSG0001
rows.name:
With Badr Stronghold to the north, and the Hilal
Stronghold where I was held, the Ganglion have the
entirety of Sylvalum under their control.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev017701_MSG0002
rows.name:
Because of that, BLADE has made virtually no progress
surveying the continent.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev017701_MSG0003
rows.name:
So not only are we clueless about the Ganglion's
movements in the region, but the fog of spore clouds
severely restricts our sight lines.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev017701_MSG0004
rows.name:
The level of danger there is on a whole other scale.
If you're planning to explore Sylvalum, make sure your
preparations are far more rigorous than usual![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev017701_MSG0010
rows.name:
My mimeosome is a wreck after the vicious torture
they subjected me to.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev017701_MSG0011
rows.name:
I've been ordered to rest until the technicians are able
to acquire the replacement parts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev017701_MSG0012
rows.name:
But I want to ignore their orders, rush back to the
front lines, and do what I can to fill in for Marla
and everyone else they killed![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev017701_MSG0013
rows.name:
But it's probably best that I don't cause any more
trouble for Defense Secretary Nagi and you guys...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev017701_MSG0014
rows.name:
Instead I'll just start preparing equipment for the day I
return to battle in my patched-up mimeosome.[ST:wait ]
